---
title: Moroccan Chicken, Lentil & Cauliflower Pie with Parmesan Mash Topping
description: No one will want to miss dinner when this irresistible veggie pie is on the menu! With a saucy chermoula-spiced lentil filling and creamy Parmesan-laced mash, it’s humble home cooking at its finest.
